<div class="title">My Struggle</div>
<div class="substance">Amphetamines - Adderall</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Addict&Exact=1">Addict</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Addict. "My Struggle: An Experience with Amphetamines - Adderall (exp18184)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Apr 16, 2007. erowid.org/exp/18184</div>

<br/>



